465	\section{Stein finiteness of global sections}
466	\label{sec:module_finite_globalSections_iter044}
467	
468	The geometric input for the wholespace Hom-finiteness carrier is Stein's theorem: on a proper integral scheme over a field, global sections are finite-dimensional.
