512	\label{sec:IsHModuleHomFinite_producer}
513	
514	We now assemble the chain: constant-sheaf/global-sections adjunction, Hom-from-$k$ evaluation, and Stein finiteness, to produce the wholespace $H^0$ Hom-finiteness instance.
